Hard water?

547
00:41:47,354 --> 00:41:50,062
Not only that,
but the raindrops change...

548
00:41:50,157 --> 00:41:53,070
into small white spots
that look like lace...

549
00:41:53,160 --> 00:41:55,265
and this is called snow.

550
