such thing as snow!

553
00:42:05,472 --> 00:42:08,851
And I do not believe
such thing as snow.

554
00:42:08,943 --> 00:42:11,389
And I do not believe
Siam is this big.

555
00:42:11,478 --> 00:42:13,389
And other countries so big.

556
00:42:13,480 --> 00:42:15,482
Siam is the biggest country
in the world!

557
00:42:15,583 --> 00:42:17,563
[ Shouting, Screaming ]
Siam!

558
00:42:22,056 --> 00:42:24,195
[ Shouts In Siamese ]

559
00:42:27,194 --> 00:42:29,902
How can school be so unscientific?

560
00:42:29,997 --> 00:42:34,036
- Well, Your Majesty,
we had a little misunderstanding.
- Ah.

561
00:42:34,134 --> 00:42:38,241
I was trying to describe snow,
and they refused to believe there is such a thing.

562
00:42:40,441 --> 00:42:44,184
- Snow?
- Snow.

563
