- From the sky, Your Majesty.
- From sky to mountaintop.

565
00:42:50,084 --> 00:42:52,121
- [ Sniffs ]
- That's right, Your Majesty.

566
00:42:52,219 --> 00:42:54,790
I remember.
I see pictures of Switzerland-

567
00:42:54,888 --> 00:42:58,665
land all white with snow.

568
00:43:00,427 --> 00:43:02,464
Who does not believe this?

569
00:43:02,563 --> 00:43:05,043
Well, Your Majesty, after all,
they've never seen it.

570
00:43:05,132 --> 00:43:07,112
Never seen?

571
00:43:07,201 --> 00:43:10,444
If they believe only what they see,
why do we have schoolroom?

572
00:43:10,537 --> 00:43:13,347
[ Shouts In Siamese ]

573
00:43:13,440 --> 00:43:17,354
Never let me hear
of not believing schoolteacher...

574
00:43:17,444 --> 00:43:21,187
whom I have bring here
at high expense-

575
00:43:22,850 --> 00:43:26,320
- twenty pounds each month.
- [ Gasping ]

576
00:43:26,420 --> 00:43:29,230
Twenty English pounds...

577
00:43:29,323 --> 00:43:31,360
sterling!

578
00:43:31,458 --> 00:43:33,438
Rise!

579
00:43:34,862 --> 00:43:37,433
I command all of you
to make most of this opportunity...

580
00:43:37,531 --> 00:43:40,307
for expensive education...

581
00:43:40,401 --> 00:43:43,439
for sake of selves and country.

582
00:43:43,537 --> 00:43:45,517
Furthermore, it is, uh-

583
00:43:45,606 --> 00:43:48,348
What, what, what?
This is not study book I have provide.

584
00:43:48,442 --> 00:43:52,913
