646
00:48:05,499 --> 00:48:07,233
Oh.

647
00:48:07,234 --> 00:48:07,473
Oh.

648
00:48:14,174 --> 00:48:16,154
You sent for me, Your Majesty?

649
00:48:22,616 --> 00:48:24,596
Your Majesty.

650
00:48:30,724 --> 00:48:34,536
Oh, Your Majesty is reading the Bible.

651
00:48:37,230 --> 00:48:39,710
Ah, Mrs. Anna.

652
00:48:39,800 --> 00:48:42,303
I think your Moses
shall have been a fool.

653
00:48:42,402 --> 00:48:45,906
- Moses?
- Moses, Moses, Moses.

654
00:48:46,006 --> 00:48:47,986
I think he shall have been a fool.

655
00:48:48,075 --> 00:48:50,112
Here it stands written by him...

656
00:48:50,210 --> 00:48:53,987
that the world was created
in six days.

657
00:48:54,081 --> 00:48:58,996
Now, you know and I know
that it took many ages to create world.

658
00:48:59,086 --> 00:49:02,295
I think he shall have been a fool
to have written so.

659
00:49:02,389 --> 00:49:04,369
What is your opinion?

660
00:49:04,458 --> 00:49:08,736
Is that why Your Majesty sent for me
at this hour of the night?

661
00:49:08,829 --> 00:49:11,810
That is not reason,
but first I wish to discuss Moses.

662
00:49:11,898 --> 00:49:14,538
Now, how am I ever to learn truth...

663
00:49:14,635 --> 00:49:17,673
if different English books
state different things?

664
00:49:19,640 --> 00:49:24,248
Your Majesty, the Bible was not written
by men of science, but by men of faith.

665
00:49:25,579 --> 00:49:28,025
<i>It was their explanation
of the miracle of creation...</i>

666
00:49:28,115 --> 00:49:32,325
which is the same miracle
whether it took six days or many centuries.

667
00:49:35,088 --> 00:49:37,068
Huh.

668
00:49:41,228 --> 00:49:43,708
I still think your Moses
shall have been a fool.

669
00:49:45,198 --> 00:49:48,771
As you wish, Your Majesty.
Now, was there something else?

670
00:49:48,869 --> 00:49:50,849
Take letter.

671
00:49:50,937 --> 00:49:53,543
A letter? Now?

672
00:49:53,640 --> 00:49:56,553
Now. When else?
Now is always best time.

673
00:49:56,643 --> 00:50:00,420
Take letter to "Mr. Lingkong" of America,
who is very scientific ruler.

674
00:50:00,514 --> 00:50:03,927
- [ Sniffs ]
- Very well, Your Majesty.

675
00:50:04,017 --> 00:50:07,260
Uh, from Phra Mana Mongkut...

676
00:50:07,354 --> 00:50:10,130
by the blessing
of the highest superagency...

677
00:50:10,223 --> 00:50:12,703
in the world of the whole universe...

678
00:50:12,793 --> 00:50:14,704
the king of Siam...

679
00:50:14,795 --> 00:50:16,775
<i>sovereign of all tributary countries...</i>

680
00:50:16,863 --> 00:50:19,434
<i>adjacent and around in every direction...</i>

681
00:50:19,533 --> 00:50:21,672
et cetera, et cetera, et cetera-

682
00:50:23,804 --> 00:50:26,478
Do you not have any respect for me?

683
00:50:27,674 --> 00:50:29,654
<i>Why do you stand over my head?</i>

684
00:50:29,743 --> 00:50:32,724
I cannot stand all the time...

685
00:50:32,813 --> 00:50:35,919
and in this country,
no one's head shall be higher than king's.

686
00:50:37,617 --> 00:50:41,622
From now on, in presence,
you shall so conduct like all other subjects.

687
00:50:41,722 --> 00:50:45,568
- You mean, on the floor?
- All subjects do so.

688
00:50:45,659 --> 00:50:47,764
I am very sorry.

689
00:50:47,861 --> 00:50:51,274
I shall try my best not to let my head
be higher than Your Majesty's...

690
00:50:51,364 --> 00:50:54,140
but I simply cannot grovel
on the floor.

691
00:50:54,234 --> 00:50:57,272
I couldn't possibly work that way
or think.

692
00:51:03,710 --> 00:51:06,714
You are very difficult woman!

693
00:51:06,813 --> 00:51:08,724
Perhaps so, Your Majesty.

694
00:51:08,815 --> 00:51:11,523
But you'll observe care
that head shall never be higher than mine.

695
00:51:11,618 --> 00:51:13,529
When I shall sit, you shall sit!

696
00:51:13,620 --> 00:51:15,531
When I shall kneel, you shall kneel...

697
00:51:15,622 --> 00:51:18,535
et cetera, et cetera, et cetera!

698
00:51:20,227 --> 00:51:22,207
Very well, Your Majesty.

699
00:51:23,563 --> 00:51:25,873
Is promise?

700
00:51:28,535 --> 00:51:30,515
Is promise.

701
00:51:30,604 --> 00:51:32,584
Good.

702
00:51:39,579 --> 00:51:43,493
To his royal presidency
of the United States in America...

703
00:51:43,583 --> 00:51:46,325
"Abrahom Lingkong"...

704
00:51:46,419 --> 00:51:49,559
um, et cetera- You fix up.

705
00:51:51,324 --> 00:51:53,804
It has occurred to us-

706
00:51:55,395 --> 00:51:58,535
You see, it has occurred to us-

707
00:52:10,010 --> 00:52:12,650
It has occurred to us
that if we shall be sending you...

708
00:52:12,746 --> 00:52:16,057
several pairs
of young male elephants...

709
00:52:16,149 --> 00:52:19,562
to be turned loose
in forest of America-

710
00:52:19,653 --> 00:52:21,792
"A-mer-i-ca"-

711
00:52:23,123 --> 00:52:25,160
we are of opinion...

712
00:52:25,258 --> 00:52:28,899
that after a while,
they shall increase in number...

713
00:52:28,995 --> 00:52:31,566
- and inhabitants of America shall be able to-
- [ Clears Throat ]

714
00:52:31,665 --> 00:52:33,702
