- Well?

715
00:52:33,800 --> 00:52:36,872
I don't think you mean
pairs of male elephants.

716
00:52:36,970 --> 00:52:39,450
How can I make letter
if you interrupt?

717
00:52:39,539 --> 00:52:44,181
And inhabitants of America shall be able
to catch and tame them...

718
00:52:44,277 --> 00:52:47,520
and use them as beasts of burden.

719
00:52:47,614 --> 00:52:50,527
Only male elephants, Your Majesty?

720
00:52:55,355 --> 00:52:57,995
You put in the details.
Good night.

721
00:53:04,364 --> 00:53:08,540
Moses. Lincoln. Elephants!

722
00:53:08,635 --> 00:53:11,548
- Groveling on the floor at 2:00 in the morning.
- Ma'am. Ma'am!

723
00:53:13,206 --> 00:53:16,813
I am Lun Tha.
You are Mrs. Anna, schoolteacher?

724
00:53:16,910 --> 00:53:19,117
Yes, but you shouldn't be-

725
00:53:19,212 --> 00:53:22,318
I must meet with Tuptim again.
Please!

726
00:53:22,415 --> 00:53:24,725
You have been seeing her here?

727
00:53:24,818 --> 00:53:26,855
Twice we have spoken.

728
00:53:26,953 --> 00:53:28,990
Each time it becomes more difficult.

729
00:53:29,089 --> 00:53:31,160
She has said you are friend
who will help us.

730
00:53:31,258 --> 00:53:33,499
Oh, no, I couldn't.

731
00:53:33,593 --> 00:53:37,200
It's much too dangerous-
not for me, but for Tuptim and you.

732
00:53:37,297 --> 00:53:39,937
You would be killed if they find you here
in the City of women.

733
00:53:40,033 --> 00:53:42,274
<i>You must /ea vs at once!</i>

734
00:53:42,369 --> 00:53:45,282
Death is not worse pain
than empty life.

735
00:53:45,372 --> 00:53:47,409
Please, Mrs. Anna.

736
00:53:47,507 --> 00:53:50,818
I'm sorry, Lun Tha.
There's nothing I can do.

737
00:54:10,430 --> 00:54:12,410
Wait there.

738
00:55:14,828 --> 00:55:16,739
Tuptim.

739
00:55:16,830 --> 00:55:18,741
Oh, Lun Tha.

740
00:55:18,832 --> 00:55:21,642
Seeing you this way is not enough.

741
00:55:22,736 --> 00:55:25,808
There is nothing we can do.

742
